node.text:
25 laps around the sun. Besides all the bs, life is amazing lol. I lost friends and seen people not make it here. A lot of people don’t. And if they do, probably not like this. So Shoutout to God🙏🏾 for bringing me here. My friends, my family everything I’ve been blessed with.....sometimes I feel like I got it all. But for the most part I know I still got a lot more to do. This 25th lap is a different run, it’s pivotal. I reached this point in this position for a reason. I Think about the people out there with crazy skills, gifts and talents, but never have the courage to broadcast it .... so they die with it.....a lot of them before 25! This new run I’m on I promised myself everything I find and believe in private I will show the world in public.
Including this book. I found a niche for writing and telling stories early on.... but never really went past essays for school and captions. I still didn’t know if I wanted to put it out, but I know I can either put it out and change lives, or die with it and keep everything the same. So here it is, on my 25th, my first book is officially available to lock in. My biggest birthday wish is for all of you to read it, relate, and allow the content to change your life in the same ways if not better it did for mine. Thank you to everybody who’s showed me genuine love and support thus far. I love you and I’m with you forever. God is the greatest! #linkinbio #BTDAY #itllallmakesense

You literally have to PAY attention. The cost is the time. However long it takes for you to stay locked in and focused on something until you get results people can’t ignore. When you’re laser focused some of the things you do, say or think about ...... you KNOW FOR A FACT other people are not. Go harder and focus more, you said you where going to be a millionaire.....IDK who needed to hear this
